{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_53_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依 3話 親に紹介って",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十一月十一日　夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.3333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2566.6666667,
          "startTime": 3.3666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4366.666666700001,
          "startTime": 5.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ここをこうして……最後に……うん、完璧ね\n出来たわよ、瑠依。もう動いていいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "凄い……とっても可愛いです\n莉央さん、こういうことも得意なんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1666658402,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3766.667302400002,
          "startTime": 17.6666664124
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "昔から、よく葵の髪をセットしてあげることが\nあったから。興味もあったし、覚えたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "あの子ってば、面倒くさがって髪を乾かさなかったり\nぼさぼさのまま出掛けようとしたりして大変だったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、確かお二人が出会った頃って、葵はまだ小学生\nだったんですよね。私も昔はよく母にしてもらいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "まるで私がお母さんみたいな言い方じゃない\nまったく。でも、私もそうだったから分かるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "お店の定休日に、たまに遊びに連れてってくれてね\n出掛ける前に髪を結んでくれて、嬉しかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "素敵な思い出ですね。それに、莉央さんとこういう話が\n出来るのは、なんだか感慨深いです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7865872151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロにいた頃は、あまり話すこともなかったからね\n意外と常識外れで、破天荒なところも知らなかったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、なんだかこういう話をしていると\nお母さんの顔が見たくなってきちゃうわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。誕生日なので、電話はもらったんですが\n母も仕事があるので、そこまで長くは話せなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん。じゃあ、今から会いに行ってくれば？\n瑠依の実家、そこまで遠くないんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、そうですけど、これから寮で私のために\nパーティーがあるんですよ？　それに、会うなら――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "細かいことはいいのよ。貴方は今日の主役なんだから\nたまには好き勝手しても、バチは当たらないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん……。はい。私、ママに会ってきます……！\n莉央さんも一緒に行きませんか？　紹介したいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "え？　しょ、紹介？　なんでそうなるのよ\n親に紹介って……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに素敵な先輩がいるんだよって、自慢したく\nなっちゃいました。それに母もアイドルが好きですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、今なら会社にいるはずなので\n実家に行かなくても会えるかも！　連絡してみますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.8999949138,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4800.005086200003,
          "startTime": 154.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_53_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "いや、家族水入らずで会いなさいよ！　そういえば朝倉\n社長も急に無茶を言うとこがあったわね。よく似てるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.4666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}